## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-156">경우는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> 속성에 할당 되는 이전에 만든 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 가 복제 되지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-156">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-157">대신,는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> 이전에 만든에 대 한 참조를 유지 관리 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-157">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-158">업데이트 작업을 하는 동안 경우 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> 설정 되어 있지 않고 기본 키 정보에는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>를 사용할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 자동으로 생성 하는 클래스는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>는 조정하는데필요한추가명령을<xref:System.Data.DataSet>데이터베이스에 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-158">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-159">이 위해 설정 된 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-159">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-160">키 열에 대 한 정보가 있어야 생성 논리는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-160">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-161">자세한 내용은 참조 [commandbuilder 생성 명령을](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-161">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-162">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 설정 하 고는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 및 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-162">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-163">이미 만든 것으로 간주 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-163">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  

```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   

  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  

  ' Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd  

  ' Create the DeleteCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn)  

  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  

  da.DeleteCommand = cmd  

  Return da  
End Function  
```  

```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  

  // Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  

  // Create the DeleteCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn);  

  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  

  da.DeleteCommand = cmd;  

  return da;  
}  
```



## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-166">때는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 속성에 할당 되는 이전에 만든 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 개체는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 가 복제 되지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-166">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-167">대신, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 이전에 만든에 대 한 참조를 유지 관리 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-167">Instead, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-168">업데이트 작업을 하는 동안 경우 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 설정 되어 있지 않고 기본 키 정보에는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>를 사용할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 자동으로 생성 하는 클래스 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>를 조정 하는 데 필요한 추가 명령을 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 에 데이터베이스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-168">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-169">이 위해 설정 된 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-169">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-170">키 열에 대 한 정보가 있어야 생성 논리는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-170">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-171">자세한 내용은 참조 [commandbuilder 생성 명령을](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-171">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="df98e-172">이 명령 실행 하 여 행이 반환 하는 경우 이러한 행에 추가할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 설정 하는 방법에 따라는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> 의 속성은 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-172">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be added to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-173">지정 된 열을 업데이트 하는 경우는 `LONG RAW` 데이터 형식 값을 입력 하면 예외가 throw 됩니다 `NULL` 열에 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-173">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-174">Oracle `LONG RAW` 데이터 형식은 Oracle 버전 8.0의에서 사용 되지 않는 형식입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-174">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-175">이 오류를 방지 하려면 사용 된 `BLOB` 데이터 형식 대신 `LONG RAW`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-175">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-176">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 설정 하 고는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 및 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-176">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-177">이미 만든 것으로 간주 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-177">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  

```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   

  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  

  ' Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd  

  ' Create the InsertCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  

  da.InsertCommand = cmd  

  Return da  
End Function  
```  

```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  

  // Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  

  // Create the InsertCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " +  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName");  

  da.InsertCommand = cmd;  

  return da;  
}  
```



## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-200">때 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 할당 되는 이전에 만든 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 가 복제 되지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-200">When <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-201">대신,는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 이전에 만든에 대 한 참조를 유지 관리 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-201">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-202">경우 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 모든 행을 반환 하지 않는에 테이블이 추가 되는 **데이터 집합**, 예외가 발생 하지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-202">If <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> does not return any rows, no tables are added to the **DataSet**, and no exception is raised.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-203">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 설정 하 고는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 및 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-203">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-204">이미 만든 것으로 간주 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-204">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  

```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   

  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  

  ' Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd  

  ' Create the InsertCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (pDeptNo, pDName)", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  

  da.InsertCommand = cmd  

  Return da  
End Function  
```  

```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  

  // Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  

  // Create the InsertCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " +  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName");  

  da.InsertCommand = cmd;  

  return da;  
}  
```



## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-244">때 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> 할당 되는 이전에 만든 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 가 복제 되지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-244">When <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-245">대신,는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> 이전에 만든에 대 한 참조를 유지 관리 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-245">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-246">업데이트 작업을 하는 동안 경우 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> 설정 되어 있지 않고 기본 키 정보에는 **데이터 집합**를 사용할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> 클래스를 자동으로 생성할 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, 하는 데 필요한 추가 명령 조정 된 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 데이터베이스에 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-246">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the **DataSet**, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-247">이 위해 설정 된 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-247">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-248">키 열에 대 한 정보가 있어야 생성 논리는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-248">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-249">자세한 내용은 참조 [commandbuilder 생성 명령을](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-249">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="df98e-250">이러한 행이이 명령 실행 하 여 행이 반환 하는 경우와 병합 될 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Data.DataSet> 설정 하는 방법에 따라는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> 의 속성은 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-250">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be merged with the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-251">지정 된 열을 업데이트 하는 경우는 `LONG RAW` 데이터 형식 값을 입력 하면 예외가 throw 됩니다 `NULL` 열에 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-251">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-252">Oracle `LONG RAW` 데이터 형식은 Oracle 버전 8.0의에서 사용 되지 않는 형식입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-252">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-253">이 오류를 방지 하려면 사용 된 `BLOB` 데이터 형식 대신 `LONG RAW`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-253">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="df98e-254">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> 설정 하 고는 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> 및 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-254">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df98e-255">이미 만든 것으로 간주 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df98e-255">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  

```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   

  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  

  ' Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = pDName AND Loc = pLoc", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd  

  ' Create the UpdateCommand.  

  cmd = New OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = pDeptNo, DName = pDName " & _  
                       "WHERE DeptNo = poldDeptNo", conn)  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  

  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  

  da.UpdateCommand = cmd  

  Return da  
End Function  
```  

```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  

  // Create the SelectCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = pDName AND Loc = pLoc", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  

  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  

  // Create the UpdateCommand.  

  cmd = new OracleCommand("UPDATE Dept SET DeptNo = pDeptNo, DName = pDName " +  
                       "WHERE DeptNo = poldDeptNo", conn);  

  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName");  

  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("poldDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  

  da.UpdateCommand = cmd;  

  return da;  
}  
```
